{"id":582007,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【立此存照】新浪微博审查过滤习金会图片示/","date":"2018-03-31T09:39:02Z","modified":"2018-03-31T17:06:08Z","title":"【立此存照】新浪微博审查过滤“习金会”图片示例","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>近日，一日文推号分享了一张日本媒体报道习近平与金正恩会面新闻的截屏，截屏中媒体的配词大意为“在百忙之中，习近平像亲哥哥一样招待我，十分感谢”，该推号对此吐槽“亲哥哥已经被你杀了”（大意），引来热传 (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dorodayo/status/978969194304696320\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">原推链接</a>)。</p>\n<p>随后，有微博用户分享了日文推号的调侃截图，然而这张图片很快就被新浪微博进行了过滤屏蔽处理。在用图片识别对特定内容进行审查的现象<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/04/%e5%a5%87%e5%ae%a2%e8%b5%84%e8%ae%af-%e7%a0%94%e7%a9%b6%e5%8f%91%e7%8e%b0%e5%be%ae%e4%bf%a1%e4%bc%9a%e5%ae%a1%e6%9f%a5%e5%9b%be%e5%83%8f/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">在微信上也相当常见</a>，但一般只有用中国大陆手机号注册的微信才会成为审查对象。</p>\n<p><strong>习金会图片被新浪微博屏蔽前：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_582009\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582009\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"256\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片2.jpg 1512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片2-300x146.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片2-768x374.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片2-1024x498.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>被屏蔽后：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_582008\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582008\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片1.jpg 1216w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片1-300x162.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片1-768x416.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博屏蔽图片1-1024x554.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>被屏蔽图片：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/习近平-金正恩.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-582010\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/习近平-金正恩.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/习近平-金正恩.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/习近平-金正恩-300x289.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,27949],"tags":[9980,26869,9553,8616,20895,22751,14615]}